@startuml
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "Discord AI Bot" {
  usecase "Chat with AI\nvia @mention" as UC1
  usecase "Web Search\n(brave_search)" as UC2
  usecase "Browse Local Files\n(local_files)" as UC3
  usecase "Receive Email\nNotifications" as UC4
  usecase "Configure Jobs\nvia jobs.json" as UC5
  usecase "Switch AI Provider\nvia .env" as UC6
}

User --> UC1
User --> UC4
User --> UC5
User --> UC6
UC1 ..> UC2 : <<extend>>
UC1 ..> UC3 : <<extend>>

note right of UC2
  AI decides when to
  call tools based on
  user's question
end note

note right of UC4
  Gmail / Outlook / QQ Mail
  monitored via IMAP
  AI classifies & summarizes
end note

@enduml
